  "description": "The Vanilla-Ish texture pack with minor edits for the game.",
  "body": "# This is PixelPack.\n\n![The text 'PixelPack by WorldWidePixel' in front of colourful geometric shapes.](https://rounder.worldwidepixel.ca/?r=40&url=https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/c7dY2rRz/images/a77cfe999a8f3e3800aac9ad9a2d2dd8b48d98d4.png)\n\nThe description is going under a little bit of an overhaul. Sorry if it looks a little rough right now.\n\n<h2>❔ What is PixelPack?</h2>\n\n<p>\nIt's my personal Resource Pack. Started as a fun project back in 2020, it has grown to become my main resource pack, made to fix annoying textures.\n</p>\n\n<a href=\"https://worldwidepixel.ca/pixelpack\">\n\n<img alt=\"Also available on My Website.\" src=\"https://badger-api-staging.worldwidepixel.ca/cozy?gradientStart=22252c&gradientEnd=16181c&lineOne=Also%20available%20on&lineTwo=My%20Website&colourOne=FFFFFF&colourTwo=28cbd4&iconUrl=https://worldwidepixel.ca/img/icon512.png\" >\n\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"/mod/vistas\">\n<img src=\"https://badger-api-staging.worldwidepixel.ca/cozy?gradientStart=005ED5&gradientEnd=0051A0&lineOne=Works%20with&lineTwo=Vistas&colourOne=FFFFFF&colourTwo=30f4fe&iconUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fwsrv.nl%2F%3Furl%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Frounder.worldwidepixel.ca%252F%253Fr%253D80%2526url%253Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fcdn.modrinth.com%252Fdata%252FitzZXRxq%252F8d5f3b3d63b4200a91d58556cb9f055a3ae9a46c.webp%26output%3Dpng&format=png\" \n alt=\"Works with Vistas Mod\">\n\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"/mod/continuity\">\n<img src=\"https://badger-api-staging.worldwidepixel.ca/cozy?gradientStart=FF9525&gradientEnd=F97000&lineOne=Works%20with&lineTwo=Continuity&colourOne=FFFFFF&colourTwo=FFE330&iconUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fwsrv.nl%2F%3Furl%3D%0Ahttps%253A%252F%252Frounder.worldwidepixel.ca%252F%253Fr%253D80%2526url%253D%250Ahttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fcdn.modrinth.com%25252Fdata%25252F1IjD5062%25252Ficon.png&format=png&n=-1\" \n alt=\"Works with Vistas Mod\">\n\n</a>\n\n<h2></h2>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/c7dY2rRz/images/a017abf4f2f4eb54f186b906c59ac87ccf219b5b.png\" alt=\"a Comparison between Vanilla Minecraft and PixelPack\">\n\n<h2>➕ PixelPack includes these features:</h2>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/c7dY2rRz/images/a20e6c521407fe62ed1808234babb78825be8979.png\" alt=\"PixelPack has improved the textures for Bricks and various Stones.\">\n\n<p></p>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/c7dY2rRz/images/36ced48f447d7ea3e871d3ac2650f4dfdf8f45af.png\" alt=\"PixelPack adds a Golden Crown. It's mainly for fun.\">\n\n<p></p>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/c7dY2rRz/images/8411a2c3aa863e64a22120969ee2e79be8397cc2.png\" alt=\"PixelPack improves the Ore Textures, making them easier to see.\">\n\n<p></p>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/c7dY2rRz/images/5762d3cb491df7a48fe041b1acedb070c998d1ca.png\" alt=\"PixelPack adds a new Title Panorama.\">\n\n<p />\n\n<h2>Enjoy! - Pixel</h2>\n\n<p>PixelPack is provided under a MPL-2.0 License.</p>",
